{
  "stem": "23498.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were lucky to have that one room, but then when the conditions were worse, that was this is mine and this is yours.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father started to look for something on our own.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he found a room-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a-- a big kitchen and a small room in Zamenhof Street.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was in-- in the big ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was very lucky because next door was a bakery so the whole wall was warm.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't need any-- anything to warm us up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when the action started, the Germans started to-- to take people to Umschlagplatz, you know, then from there by train to concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father discovered that there is that one little room can be a hiding place from us-- for us because that was I recall it was a enormous antique wardrobe.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father took the inner wall out and put some screws, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He knew about it, and he tie it up from inside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So in other words, when we went there he put the-- the missing part, it-- nothing was visible.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the frame of the door was lower than the wardrobe so no one could even suggest that there is another room.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Also what was lucky, it was a coincident that in that little room there was a window high up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was sort of half of the window, and they couldn't see us and it was going to the next number.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like this was number nine, so that was 11, you see?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it was a perfect hiding place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And people every time it was action, you know, people were hiding anywhere, anywhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And mostly they were running up, up to these-- you know, under the roof.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
